{"tid":598161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"色慾校服情侶　平台公然互摷","createTime":"2018-03-19T09:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T05:08:48.000Z","uid":28366,"like":29,"dislike":154,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"9a956f4c3df290f35aa7db63749e96cedff453b5","tid":598161,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20070131/large/31ls1p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20070131%2Flarge%2F31ls1p6.jpg&h=b10a1379&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20070131/large/31ls1p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20070131%2Flarge%2F31ls1p7.jpg&h=7da013e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20070131/large/31ls1p9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20070131%2Flarge%2F31ls1p9.jpg&h=682a01d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n少男少女情竇初開，拍拖之際情到濃時，或許不能自我控制，出現激情行為。近日就有網民直擊身穿校服的學生情侶公然在公園纏綿，雙方手口並用，行為大膽開放令人側目，不少網民看過照片後嘩然，批評學生德育水平每下愈況。<br />\n<br />\n「個男仔係咁搞，個女仔度扮到欲拒還迎，點知最後個女仔主動番，好彩佢除衫之前有保安員行過，唔係真係無眼睇！」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>少男將手伸入裙內</strong><br />\n<br />\n網民 atvreality在香港討論區發放多幅相片和短片，內容都是一對校服情侶的纏綿情況，男生穿藍色冷衫、灰色長褲，女學生則是一條藍色連身校裙，繫上紅色領帶。<br />\n由照片可見，該對學生情侶纏綿時非常肉緊，女方躺在男方大腿上，男方一度將手伸入女方裙內。「佢不顧樓上或附近大廈有住戶，公然於屋苑平台互相挑逗。」網友 atvreality形容兩人敗壞道德風氣。<br />\n這幾張激情照片激發網民議論，批評兩人不知廉恥，「好激呀！家情侶真係開放。」網民 happy1202則說：「點解家後生仔女會搞成咁，我真係要好好睇實我個女先得呀！」<br />\n育評議會副主席何漢權認為近年中學生行為問題越來越嚴重，這對小情侶行為越軌，師長應輔導他們建立健康價值觀，如有需要應報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180319/6768807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180319%2F6768807&d=dYNBpw77B42fMm44Tyl9p7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=d2fc86c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180319%2F6768807&h=f0d3361d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180319/6768807</a>"},{"pid":"e44e710890fc391fb9a6dd663cfea94e9425a042","tid":598161,"uid":63909,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f87825ff0b93fa2a74a91fa6e433b944471006","tid":598161,"uid":93266,"like":158,"dislike":6,"score":152,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:35:06.000Z","msg":"影相條友識唔識影相架 ?"},{"pid":"e55d8d131de8b7f6a0d0532426dd5d8d5f7e46d9","tid":598161,"uid":65371,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:35:14.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦"},{"pid":"efcd7132a5770fa8d632cb1e33b06cb4911ef613","tid":598161,"uid":56533,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:36:01.000Z","msg":"青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92df05d65e98ce1cf2932647275fee3b99a9b345","tid":598161,"uid":70439,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:36:07.000Z","msg":"Ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3abbf28104f91db50a566387be52f6539c136fb","tid":598161,"uid":47359,"like":173,"dislike":3,"score":170,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:36:19.000Z","msg":"以為舊聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f9a037ed86f0730ef8514c8e9f1151da458706","tid":598161,"uid":61675,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:37:10.000Z","msg":"又係呢個平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080f39699c4510446b0b9a85bfce141ce3c1c6cd","tid":598161,"uid":90863,"like":13,"dislike":6,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:37:39.000Z","m